imdb.plot outline: Jen and Barb, two business-savvy moms and longtime best friends, set out to flip homes in Southern California. From house shopping and deal-making to staging and money-managing, the aim to master every trick of the home flipping trade. Combined with their experience as moms, Jen and Barb hope, in the end, to build the perfect family home and earn a hefty profit on the resale. But they quickly learn that in the world of the fix and flip, nothing comes without a fight.
